  "texts": [
    "In this study, we introduced and used a modified VGG16 model to identify kidney stones in KUB x-ray images.",
    "The results of our experiments show that the modified VGG16 model has an accuracy of 97.41% in identifying kidney stones within KUB x-ray images.",
    "DL models like VGG16 can be perceived as \"black boxes\" because they lack transparency or prediction fairness.",
    "In addressing this issue, the study employs the XAI technique LRP to elucidate the model's predictions, enhancing users' comprehension of the rationale behind the decision-making process.",
    "This approach provides a transparent and effective solution for arriving at definitive diagnostic conclusions, reducing the time needed for diagnosis and enhancing diagnostic accuracy."
  ],
